# The move to the nearest iron ore resource patch has been executed successfully.

# Now, I will proceed to harvest iron ore from this resource patch. I will aim to collect a reasonable quantity, specifically 10 units of iron ore.

# Attempting to harvest 10 units of iron ore from the closest iron ore resource patch.

harvested_iron = harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.IronOre), quantity=10)
assert harvested_iron == 10, f"Expected to harvest 10 iron ore, but harvested {harvested_iron} instead."  # Ensure we harvested the correct amount.
print(f"Inventory updated to: {inspect_inventory()}")  # Display updated inventory.
